{"tid":2354173,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"楊穎宇指被冒名寄信至考評局　內含桑拿廣告、「黃色事業」字句　批評信件污衊人格","createTime":"2021-01-05T09:15:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T03:40:54.000Z","uid":240362,"like":21,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"eaeb599f88288bd380b1b93c42a19b479d303b8a","tid":2354173,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T09:15:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/20200105-0820copy_sE3cW_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F20200105-0820copy_sE3cW_1200x0.png&h=f1acc806&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前考評局歷史科經理楊穎宇因文憑試歷史題風波離職，他表示昨接獲前同事告知，考評局收到處名「楊穎宇」的信件，信件內容為桑拿浴室廣告，當中包括多張身穿三點式泳衣的女性照片，又寫有「我，楊穎宇，前考評局高官，已經轉行，加入黃色事業，介紹好嘢給你們」。楊穎宇批評，「對家冒我嘅名寄呢啲信，係想污衊我人格&hellip;亦反映（歷史題風波）冤情有幾深！」<br />\n<br />\n楊穎宇表示，該信件原寄往考評局於灣仔修頓中心的辦公室，亦即他以往工作的地方，信封面寫上是人事部收，亦有註明是由「楊穎宇」寄出。楊穎宇稱，同事當時覺得奇怪，就向他查詢，惟他並沒有向考評局寄出任何信件，同事於是將信件轉交予他。<br />\n<br />\n楊穎宇向《立場》展示該封信件的內容，一半篇幅為桑拿浴室廣告，當中包括多張身穿三點式泳衣的女性照片，另一半則為《東方日報》12 月 25 日一則有關楊穎宇批評考評局因政治需要曲解題目的剪報。另外，該封信件寫有「我，楊穎宇，前考評局高官，已經轉行，加入黃色事業，介紹好嘢給你們」、「向教育界及各好友推介」，旁邊列出 10 名人士的名稱及地址。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%A5%8A%E7%A9%8E%E5%AE%87%E6%8C%87%E8%A2%AB%E5%86%92%E5%90%8D%E5%AF%84%E4%BF%A1%E8%87%B3%E8%80%83%E8%A9%95%E5%B1%80-%E5%85%A7%E5%90%AB%E6%A1%91%E6%8B%BF%E5%BB%A3%E5%91%8A-%E9%BB%83%E8%89%B2%E4%BA%8B%E6%A5%AD-%E5%AD%97%E5%8F%A5-%E6%89%B9%E8%A9%95%E4%BF%A1%E4%BB%B6%E6%B1%A1%E8%A1%8A%E4%BA%BA%E6%A0%BC/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25A5%258A%25E7%25A9%258E%25E5%25AE%2587%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2586%2592%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%25AF%2584%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E8%2587%25B3%25E8%2580%2583%25E8%25A9%2595%25E5%25B1%2580-%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%2590%25AB%25E6%25A1%2591%25E6%258B%25BF%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E5%2591%258A-%25E9%25BB%2583%25E8%2589%25B2%25E4%25BA%258B%25E6%25A5%25AD-%25E5%25AD%2597%25E5%258F%25A5-%25E6%2589%25B9%25E8%25A9%2595%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E4%25BB%25B6%25E6%25B1%25A1%25E8%25A1%258A%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25A0%25BC%2F&d=QL2FFPepynYtbGyOTzoAG4%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=5e218ea8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25A5%258A%25E7%25A9%258E%25E5%25AE%2587%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2586%2592%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%25AF%2584%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E8%2587%25B3%25E8%2580%2583%25E8%25A9%2595%25E5%25B1%2580-%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%2590%25AB%25E6%25A1%2591%25E6%258B%25BF%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E5%2591%258A-%25E9%25BB%2583%25E8%2589%25B2%25E4%25BA%258B%25E6%25A5%25AD-%25E5%25AD%2597%25E5%258F%25A5-%25E6%2589%25B9%25E8%25A9%2595%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E4%25BB%25B6%25E6%25B1%25A1%25E8%25A1%258A%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25A0%25BC%2F&h=5c6794ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%A5%8A%E7%A9%8E%E5%AE%87%E6%8C%87%E8%A2%AB%E5%86%92%E5%90%8D%E5%AF%84%E4%BF%A1%E8%87%B3%E8%80%83%E8%A9%95%E5%B1%80-%E5%85%A7%E5%90%AB%E6%A1%91%E6%8B%BF%E5%BB%A3%E5%91%8A-%E9%BB%83%E8%89%B2%E4%BA%8B%E6%A5%AD-%E5%AD%97%E5%8F%A5-%E6%89%B9%E8%A9%95%E4%BF%A1%E4%BB%B6%E6%B1%A1%E8%A1%8A%E4%BA%BA%E6%A0%BC/</a>"},{"pid":"7864ca709a475f166d30716bc92c5e34fbba7853","tid":2354173,"uid":284432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T09:22:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"000212626512db0073c6c0537c898d51b0f91710","tid":2354173,"uid":284432,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T09:25:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"34ed0f13984f9b1796ad948d17977b6e0d64fc28","tid":2354173,"uid":116615,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T09:28:46.000Z","msg":"邊個廢老咁得閒剪報紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15ea84f367c987f48e92f955d8af3481e5bfeac4","tid":2354173,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy